					"value": "<p>Tino can use Extend as part of his retributive strike.</p><hr><p><strong>Trigger</strong> An enemy damages your ally, and both are within 15 feet of you</p><hr><p>You protect your ally and strike your foe. The ally gains resistance to all damage against the triggering damage equal to 2 + your level. If the foe is within reach, make a melee Strike against it.</p><p>If Tino hits with his Retributive Strike, the target takes @Damage[3[persistent,spirit]] damage.</p><p>If Tino's Retributive Strike against the triggering creature doesn't critically miss, that creature meets the requirements for Tino to use Defiant Shove until the end of his next turn.</p>",
					"gm": ""
				},
